textBeforeTable: DOOM 4. RAGE and This tweet indicates the game will be using an all new engine, which we would guess is id's Tech 5 engine being created for this image from the trailer. The Elder Scrolls Facebook page invites you to join the elder council, also offering The Elder Scrolls Website has a teaser trailer for the game, which also concludes with that November 11 release date. On a related note, The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim, the next game in The Elder Scrolls series was announced at last night's video game awards, as the tweet says: "For all those who have been asking, TESV, sequel to Oblivion, has been announced. Skyrim will be here on 11.11.11.
